data.description: This home is situated on a tree-lined lot on 2/3 acre so allows for a private setting yet is located near restaurants and shopping. You must see this East Davenport 4 bedroom, 3 bath with lovely hardwood floors and large open updated kitchen.  4 bedrooms upstairs (one offers laundry hookups so have upstairs laundry) plus full bath.  Main floor has a large living room, kitchen, dining room, office area, plus an updated full bath.  The finished basement has rec room and a full bath plus loads of storage.  The outdoor space is where the uniqueness of this property shows.  Huge private lot, large deck, tons of parking, and an oversized garage with both front and back garage doors!
